        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This rough metal staff is pitted and sandblasted, with thousands of nigh-imperceptible sand crystals embedded in its surface.</p>\n<p>While carrying the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Occultism checks to identify aberrations and oozes native to the Darklands.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Know Direction]{Know Direction}</em>\n<p><strong>1st</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Create Water]{Create Water}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Purify Food and Drink]{Purify Food and Drink}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Unseen Servant]{Unseen Servant}</em></p></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Darkvision]{Darkvision}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Endure Elements]{Endure Elements}</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Earthbind]{Earthbind}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Neutralize Poison]{Neutralize Poison}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Wanderer's Guide]{Wanderer's Guide}</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Air Walk]{Air Walk}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Hallucinatory Terrain]{Hallucinatory Terrain}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Rope Trick]{Rope Trick}</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Pillars of Sand]{Pillars of Sand}</em> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Veil]{Veil}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
        },
